Bookley Key Trainer — third-party assets and attributions

Word list (Single-word mode)
----------------------------
assets/wordlist.txt is derived from the EFF Long Wordlist
("eff_large_wordlist.txt") published by the Electronic Frontier Foundation.
Only the word column is used; the dice-roll numbers were dropped.

  Source:  https://www.eff.org/dice
