Fonts
-----
No third-party font files are bundled; the app uses egui's built-in fonts
(egui itself bundles them under their own open licenses). If a font is ever
added under assets/ and embedded, record its name and license here.

Reference: AI-writing idiosyncrasy taxonomy
-------------------------------------------
The bundled novelist skill cites the LAMP-corpus taxonomy of AI-writing tics:
arXiv:2409.14509. This is a citation only; no text from the paper is bundled.
